001package gbw.melange.common.events.observability;
002
003/**
004 * Promises not to throw exceptions during runtime.
005 *
006 * @param <T>
007 * @author GustavBW
008 * @version $Id: $Id
009 */
010@FunctionalInterface
011public interface IPristineBiConsumer<T> extends UndeterminedBiConsumer<T> {
012    /**
013     * <p>accept.</p>
014     *
015     * @param old a T object
016     * @param newer a T object
017     */
018    void accept(T old, T newer);
019}
